reviewText: Gilmore Girls is my favorite show.  I have watched the DVDs so many times.  Witty writing, fantastic actors, and engaging dialogue.  These two seasons are my favorites: Rori's senior year of high school and freshman year of college.
Title: Gilmore Girls: The Complete Seasons 3-4

reviewText: Loved them! Arrived undamaged and a slight delay due to weather conditions. I could not wait to catch up on the Gilmore Girls since I have been watching season one for over a month every night (that's the only one I had).
Title: Gilmore Girls: The Complete Seasons 3-4
